1. *Nered* je zaustavljen čovek zbog sumnje da je počinio krivično delo. (The man was arrested *for suspicion* of having committed a crime.)

2. *Neređe* je ujedinjeno u borbi za prava ljudi. (The *unlike* were united in the fight for human rights.) 

3. *Neređem* je obeležen dolazak novih ljudi u našu zajednicu. (The *arrival* of new people in our community was marked.) 

4. Ovo je mesto gde se *nered* vidi. (This is the place where *disorder* is seen.) 

5. Policija je uspostavila *nered* na ulici. (The police established *order* on the street.)